OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781381159
OL,3,CIs Elon Musk about to become the
OL,4,Cworld's first trillionaire?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News multimedia producer
OL,7,FConnor Parker
OL,9,FSpaceX, Elon Musk's conglomerate of
OL,10,Fspace and AI companies, is set to be
OL,11,Flisted on the stock market on Friday,
OL,12,Fand it could make him the world's
OL,13,Ffirst trillionaire.
OL,15,FBut while it may look rosy for Musk,
OL,16,Fthe stock itself has sent alarm bells
OL,17,Faround Wall Street due to the
OL,18,Funprecedented valuation of the
OL,19,Fbusiness and the way Musk has been
OL,20,Fable to demand special privileges for
OL,21,Fthe listing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
