FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781381159
OL,3,CIs Elon Musk about to become the
OL,4,Cworld's first trillionaire?
OL,6,FOver half a billion shares are being
OL,7,Fput up for sale on Friday, at a sale
OL,8,Fprice of $135 (#100) a piece, and with
OL,9,FMusk already worth almost $800bn, the
OL,10,Fprofits from the SpaceX listing could
OL,11,Fmake him the world's first
OL,12,Ftrillionaire by the weekend.
OL,14,FThe scale of the listing is also
OL,15,Funprecedented. SpaceX is aiming for a
OL,16,Fvaluation of $1.77 trillion. Only six
OL,17,Fcompanies in the S&P 500 are currently
OL,18,Fworth more, with Nvidia at the top at
OL,19,F$5.2 trillion.
OL,21,FWhy is SpaceX going public?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781381159
OL,3,CIs Elon Musk about to become the
OL,4,Cworld's first trillionaire?
OL,6,FMusk has claimed he is taking SpaceX
OL,7,Fpublic by listing the company on the
OL,8,Fstock market in order to raise funds
OL,9,Ffor SpaceX's extremely ambitious goals.
OL,11,FAmong SpaceX's dreams is establishing
OL,12,Fa million-person colony on Mars.
OL,14,FBut in the short term, Musk has said
OL,15,Fthe funding will be used to put
OL,16,F100,000 next-generation Starlink
OL,17,Fsatellites into orbit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781381159
OL,3,CIs Elon Musk about to become the
OL,4,Cworld's first trillionaire?
OL,6,FThese satellites will be faster
OL,7,Fversions of the current Starlink
OL,8,Fsatellites and will expand and speed
OL,9,Fup their internet provider services.
OL,11,FMusk has also said he hopes to use the
OL,12,Ftechnology from the new satellites to
OL,13,Feventually launch "data centres in
OL,14,Fspace."
OL,16,FHe has these could be a "massive new
OL,17,Fgrowth base and you need capital for
OL,18,Fthat," but although data centres are
OL,19,Fthe craze right now, the ability to
OL,20,Fhost them in space has not yet been
OL,21,Fproven.
