CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781381159
OL,3,CIs Elon Musk about to become the
OL,4,Cworld's first trillionaire?
OL,6,FWhy are some people unhappy?
OL,8,FSome big investors are unhappy.
OL,10,FOfficials from pension funds for
OL,11,Ffirefighters, teachers and other
OL,12,Fworkers in California and New York
OL,13,Fsent a letter to SpaceX last month
OL,14,Fdecrying some of the provisions in its
OL,15,FIPO, including the "super voting
OL,16,Fshares," mandatory arbitration of
OL,17,Fshareholder claims instead of the
OL,18,Fpossibility of lawsuits and how much
OL,19,Fpower Musk will hold over the company.
OL,26,@wD@TOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781381159
OL,3,CIs Elon Musk about to become the
OL,4,Cworld's first trillionaire?
OL,6,FThe stock is also viewed as a risky
OL,7,Fbet, but many risk-averse funds like
OL,8,Fpension funds may end up owning the
OL,9,Fstock anyway.
OL,11,FThis is because SpaceX has negotiated
OL,12,Fits way into several indexes, like the
OL,13,Fpopular Nasdaq, which recently changed
OL,14,Fits rules to allow some businesses to
OL,15,Fappear on its index as soon as they
OL,16,Flist on the stock market, rather than
OL,17,Fbeing forced to wait a year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781381159
OL,3,CIs Elon Musk about to become the
OL,4,Cworld's first trillionaire?
OL,6,FThis means many pension funds, which
OL,7,Fhold index funds that automatically
OL,8,Fbuy stocks after they get included in
OL,9,Fcertain indexes, will end up with some
OL,10,FSpaceX stock.
OL,12,FThe popular S&P 500 has retained its
OL,13,Fone-year wait rule, and so SpaceX will
OL,14,Fnot appear on its index for at least a
OL,15,Fyear.
