PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781381159
OL,3,CIs Elon Musk about to become the
OL,4,Cworld's first trillionaire?
OL,6,FBut there are risks, when Musk
OL,7,Frevealed the company's finances
OL,8,Fearlier this year as part of the
OL,9,Frequirement of becoming a public
OL,10,Fbusiness.
OL,12,FAnalysts said the company's space
OL,13,Fbusiness was making less than
OL,14,Fexpected, and its AI business was
OL,15,Fmaking a loss, something you would not
OL,16,Fexpect from the largest stock listing
OL,17,Fever.
OL,19,FLots of people are going to get rich
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
