FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781381159
OL,3,CIs Elon Musk about to become the
OL,4,Cworld's first trillionaire?
OL,6,FWhile Musk's trillionaire status is
OL,7,Fthe headline part of SpaceX's listing,
OL,8,Fmany businesses and individuals will
OL,9,Fprofit on Friday.
OL,11,FMost current and former SpaceX
OL,12,Femployees are expected to earn over a
OL,13,Fmillion dollars, with the top 400 of
OL,14,Fthem expected to rake in over $100m.
OL,16,FBanks and brokerage firms are expected
OL,17,Fto rake in millions on the fees they
OL,18,Fget for handling stock transactions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781381159
OL,3,CIs Elon Musk about to become the
OL,4,Cworld's first trillionaire?
OL,6,FMusk has also set aside a larger
OL,7,Fpercentage than normal for stocks to
OL,8,Fbe bought by retail investors, i.e.
OL,9,Fthe average person, but whether they
OL,10,Fwill make any money is yet to be seen.
OL,12,FSpaceX isn't the only colossal market
OL,13,Fdebut investors are now bracing for.
OL,14,FEarlier this week, Anthropic submitted
OL,15,Fa confidential filing with the US
OL,16,FSecurities and Exchange Commission to
OL,17,Fofficially start its own IPO clock.
OL,19,FOpenAI has not yet reported filing the
OL,20,Finitial SEC paperwork, but an IPO from
OL,21,Fthe ChatGPT maker is widely expected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
